'''Miguel João de Andrade Hurst''' (yavutse ku ya 6 Kamena 1967), uzwi cyane nka '''Miguel Hurst''', ni umukinnyi wa filimi muri [[Angola]] akaba n'umuyobozi wa filimi ukomoka mu [[Abadage|Budage]] no muri [[Porutigali|Porutugali]].<ref>https://www.researchgate.net/publication/260790046_E-Participation_in_Portuguese_local_governments_evaluation_of_deployment_and_adherence_of_Web_20_technologies</ref>  Azwi cyane kubera uruhare muri firime''Foreign Land'', ''Le pacte du Silence'' and ''Filhos do Vento''<ref>http://www.designindaba.com/people/miguel-hurst</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 6 Kamena 1967 i Freiburgo mu [[Budage]] arahakurira kugeza ku myaka icyenda. Kuva mu 1977 kugeza 1979, yabaga muri [[Gineya-Biso|Gineya Bissau]] hanyuma yimukira i Lisbonne, [[Porutugali]] kuva 1979 kugeza 2003<ref>https://moviefit.me/persons/145556-miguel-hurst</ref><ref>http://www.filme-aus-afrika.de/EN/film-database/persons/personen-details/w/3813/</ref>.  Muri kiriya gihe, yize mu ishuri rya Theatre na Sinema rya Lisbonne nyuma ashinga itsinda ry’imikino rya Pau Preto i Lisbonne<ref>https://leromundoemportugues.pt/miguel-hurst-o-portugues-tambem-e-nosso/</ref>. Mu 2003, yimukiye i Luanda, muri Angola maze agirwa umuyobozi w'ikigo cya Angola Institute of Audiovisual and Multimedia Cinema (IACAM)<ref>IACAM</ref>.<ref>https://cinemaportuguesmemoriale.pt/Pessoas/id/10546/t/miguel-hurst/</ref> 

== Umwuga ==
Mu 1995 yinjiye mu bakinnyi ba ''Teatro Nacional D.Maria II-Lisboa'' <ref>http://neovibe.azurewebsites.net/artist/miguel-hurst</ref>. Mu 2007, yakoze nk'umwarimu muri disipuline Intangiriro yubuhanzi muri Universidade Independente, Luanda. Hanyuma guhera mu 2005, yakoraga ku mateka yikinamico mu kigo cyigihugu gishinzwe amahugurwa yubuhanzi umwaka umwe<ref>https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0412175/mediaindex</ref>. 

Hagati ya 2010 na 2016, akora muri Goethe-Institut Angola (Instituto Cultural Alemao), aho yaje gusaba umushinga Christiane Schulte umushinga wo kwerekana umuco wa sinema wa [[Angola]].<ref>https://www.abebooks.com/book-search/author/CHRISTIAN-SCHULTE,-MIGUEL-HURST,-GABRIELE-STILLER-KERN,-WALTER-FERNANDEZ,?cm_sp=brcr-_-bdp-_-author</ref>  Yabaye umuyobozi wubuhanzi muri Semba Comunicação, akina kuri televiziyo ''Fora de Série'' .  Nyuma yaje gukorana na opera nyinshi nka ''Sede de Viver'', ''O Comba'', ''O Testamento'' na ''Minha Terra Minha Mãe'' <ref>https://thespaces.com/screen-stars-rescuing-angolas-cinemas/</ref>. Hagati aho, mu 2015, yasohoye igitabo cyitwa ''Angola Cinemas'', ku bufatanye n’umufotozi Walter Fernandes<ref>https://africasacountry.com/2015/05/angolan-cinemas-past-and-present-tense</ref>.  Nkuwashinze, umuyobozi nuyobora ibicuruzwa bya Pau Preto Theatre Group, atunganya amakinamico menshi arimo; ''Os Condenados'', ''Museu do Pau Preto'', ''Cabral'', ''Alimária'', ''Idéia Karapinha'', Quem, ''Inyenzi yo'' ''Kuririmba'' na ''Woza Albert''<ref>https://fr.allafrica.com/stories/200305080583.html</ref> . 

